Status of the E3SM-SE E3SM/DART assimilation:

DART supports assimilation using the E3SM-SE model
in the DART Classic release.  The scripting supports
E3SM release 1.2.1 and some support for release 1.5.

Contact us at dart@ucar.edu for more information.



